mk.tmdb.entity.movie

Class TMDbMovie

  • java.lang.Object
    • mk.tmdb.entity.TMDbEntity
      • mk.tmdb.entity.movie.TMDbMovieThumbnail
        • mk.tmdb.entity.movie.TMDbMovieReduced
          • mk.tmdb.entity.movie.TMDbMovie
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TMDbMovieFull

    public class TMDbMovie
extends TMDbMovieReduced
    Class that represents a Movie with limited features.
    MovieReduced class has more features than MovieThumbnail and MovieReduced classes.
    To get a more detailed class see TMDbMovieFull.
    Author:
    Mirko Polato
